      • RegistrationNumber

        public RegistrationNumber(char letter,
                          int num)
        Construct a registration number from the given letter and num.
        参数:
        letter - a single letter.
        num - a four digit number.
        抛出:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if letter is null
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if letter is not a letter or num is not a four digit number.
